&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WHY JOIN ALO?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Mindful movement. It’s at the core of why we do what we do at ALO—it’s our calling. Because mindful movement in the studio leads to better living. It changes who yogis are off the mat, making their lives and their communities better. That’s the real meaning of studio-to-street: taking the consciousness from practice on the mat and putting it into practice in life.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;OVERVIEW&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-parastyle=&quot;Normal (Web)&quot;&gt;Are you ready to make an impact&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-parastyle=&quot;Normal (Web)&quot;&gt;in&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-parastyle=&quot;Normal (Web)&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;the world of digital commerce? As a&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-parastyle=&quot;Normal (Web)&quot;&gt;Site&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-parastyle=&quot;Normal (Web)&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-parastyle=&quot;Normal (Web)&quot;&gt;Merchandising &amp;amp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-parastyle=&quot;Normal (Web)&quot;&gt;Web&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-parastyle=&quot;Normal (Web)&quot;&gt;Operations&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-parastyle=&quot;Normal (Web)&quot;&gt;Intern&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-parastyle=&quot;Normal (Web)&quot;&gt;, you will play a key role in shaping the online customer journey by ensuring product accur&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-parastyle=&quot;Normal (Web)&quot;&gt;acy,&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-parastyle=&quot;Normal (Web)&quot;&gt;mainta&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-parastyle=&quot;Normal (Web)&quot;&gt;i&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-parastyle=&quot;Normal (Web)&quot;&gt;ning&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-parastyle=&quot;Normal (Web)&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-parastyle=&quot;Normal (Web)&quot;&gt;s&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-parastyle=&quot;Normal (Web)&quot;&gt;et-up&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-parastyle=&quot;Normal (Web)&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;and tagging integrity,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-parastyle=&quot;Normal (Web)&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;and&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-parastyle=&quot;Normal (Web)&quot;&gt;optim&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-parastyle=&quot;Normal (Web)&quot;&gt;izing&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-parastyle=&quot;Normal (Web)&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;product placement and assortments across our e-commerce platform. Your strong attention to detail and analytical mindset will directly influence how customers discover and engage with our products, driving user experience, conversion, and online sales.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:true,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:true,&amp;quot;201341983&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559740&amp;quot;:240}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;The ALO internship programs starts &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;June&amp;nbsp;8th and ends&amp;nbsp;July 31st&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;. Interns will be working 40 hours a week at our Beverly Hills HQ.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;RESPONSIBILITIES&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li data-leveltext=&quot;&quot; data-font=&quot;Symbol&quot; data-listid=&quot;4&quot; data-list-defn-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;335552541&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335559685&amp;quot;:1080,&amp;quot;335559991&amp;quot;:360,&amp;quot;469769226&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;Symbol&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469769242&amp;quot;:[8226],&amp;quot;469777803&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;left&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469777804&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469777815&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;hybridMultilevel&amp;quot;}&quot; data-aria-posinset=&quot;1&quot; data-aria-level=&quot;1&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;Product Launch Preparation&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;Assist&amp;nbsp;with product setup,&amp;nbsp;product tagging,&amp;nbsp;merchandising, and launch readiness in Shopify for site updates, ensuring accuracy across all product details to&amp;nbsp;optimize&amp;nbsp;customer experience and conversion&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-leveltext=&quot;&quot; data-font=&quot;Symbol&quot; data-listid=&quot;4&quot; data-list-defn-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;335552541&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335559685&amp;quot;:1080,&amp;quot;335559991&amp;quot;:360,&amp;quot;469769226&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;Symbol&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469769242&amp;quot;:[8226],&amp;quot;469777803&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;left&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469777804&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469777815&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;hybridMultilevel&amp;quot;}&quot; data-aria-posinset=&quot;1&quot; data-aria-level=&quot;1&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;Daily Product Sorting&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;em&gt; &lt;/em&gt;Support the site merchandising team in optimizing product sorting algorithms, increasing product&amp;nbsp;discoverability,&amp;nbsp;and aligning with marketing initiatives.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-leveltext=&quot;&quot; data-font=&quot;Symbol&quot; data-listid=&quot;4&quot; data-list-defn-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;335552541&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335559685&amp;quot;:1080,&amp;quot;335559991&amp;quot;:360,&amp;quot;469769226&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;Symbol&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469769242&amp;quot;:[8226],&amp;quot;469777803&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;left&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469777804&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469777815&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;hybridMultilevel&amp;quot;}&quot; data-aria-posinset=&quot;1&quot; data-aria-level=&quot;1&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-charstyle=&quot;Strong&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Data Analysis and Insights&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-charstyle=&quot;Strong&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;Monitor site and product performance metrics, analyze customer behavior, and&amp;nbsp;identify&amp;nbsp;trends and optimization opportunities to improve site navigation, product discoverability, user experience, and conversion rates.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:true,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:true,&amp;quot;201341983&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559740&amp;quot;:240}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;QUALIFICATIONS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Currently pursuing or recently completed a degree in Marketing, Business, E-commerce or a related field&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;335551550&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335551620&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335559738&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:0}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Proficiency in Microsoft Excel with the ability to analyze data trends and create impactful presentations&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Proactive &amp;amp; driven, strong attention to detail, organizational skills, and a strategic mindset for digital merchandising&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;335551550&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335551620&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335559738&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:0}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Excellent communication and collaboration skills, with the ability to work effectively within cross-functional teams&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Experience with e-commerce platforms (e.g., Shopify, Magento), analytical tools (Google Analytics, Tableau, Heap, etc) or content management systems is a plus&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;335551550&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335551620&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335559738&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:0}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Analytical mindset with the ability to interpret data trends and contribute to strategic merchandising decisions&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Passion for e-commerce, digital marketing, and the fashion industry&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Creative problem-solving skills and the ability to contribute innovative ideas to improve customer experience&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The base pay range for this position is $25/hr-$35/hr which represents the current range for the non-exempt position. Please note that actual pay will vary based on factors including but not limited to location, experience, and performance.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bold;&quot;&gt;Eligibility:&lt;/span&gt; This internship is open to students who are &lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bold;&quot;&gt;recent graduates &lt;/span&gt;or &lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bold;&quot;&gt;current seniors&lt;/span&gt; with graduation dates in &lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bold;&quot;&gt;Spring 2025, Winter 2025, and Spring 2026&lt;/span&gt;. Unfortunately, we are &lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bold;&quot;&gt;not able to consider candidates graduating in Winter 2026 or later&lt;/span&gt; at this time.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-conclusion&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;c-scrollbar__hider&quot; data-qa=&quot;slack_kit_scrollbar&quot;&gt;
